title: Newbie's Training 1-1
description: This is a series I'm attempting to make. This series is for anyone who likes puzzles and wants to learn how to solve these puzzles, without needing to play The Witness. To start, click the circle, and then move your mouse so that the path goes to the nub, then click again. If your solution is valid, the line will glow. That's all you need to know to solve these puzzles. The rest will be up to speculation and experimentation. Good luck!
